    "text": "Woe to you!"
  },
  {
    "language": "English",
    "translator": "Muhammad Habib Shakir",
    "text": "Nearer to you (is destruction) and nearer,"
  },
  {
    "language": "English",
    "translator": "Abdullah Yusuf Ali",
    "text": "Woe to thee, (O men!), yea, woe!"
  },
  {
    "language": "English",
    "translator": "Mufti Taqi Usmani",
    "text": "(It will be said to such a man,) Woe to you, then woe to you!"
  }
